## Conclusion

This data-driven approach to employee churn prediction provides HR departments with actionable intelligence to identify at-risk employees before they leave. By implementing targeted retention strategies based on model insights, organizations can significantly reduce turnover costs and maintain a stable, productive workforce. The combination of predictive analytics and HR strategic planning creates a comprehensive retention framework that benefits both the organization and its employees.